ets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1734e7a362e75f5c857b2159021a6c15dba39971","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入瀘沽湖訓返一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個禮拜會唔會太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5ce655d5595b7e7d275682d70fd4a2394d0882","tid":219960,"uid":56761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"之前聖誕去寄住朋友屋企，係昆明機場向南坐成5個鐘車先到。個陣好想去麗江同玉龍雪山，太遠最壞要坐成12個鐘車所以冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後個朋友同我講係昆明機場可以轉機去麗江，佢話如果我一早由最北既地方一路玩落去南邊時間充裕好多"},{"pid":"f07efe26224a570c82c008dae89ce1e6dd59d8ab","tid":219960,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a49968234fc31283866ca1a995799206af3ad34","tid":219960,"uid":102863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"老母話想去香格里拉，想做孝順仔帶佢去"},{"pid":"7675a63caa02dcd524dbe960252d4b96aa8961c5","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前聖誕去寄住朋友屋企，係昆明機場向南坐成5個鐘車先到。個陣好想去麗江同玉龍雪山，太遠最壞要坐成12個鐘車所以冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後個朋友同我講係昆明機場可以轉機去麗江，佢話如果我一早由最北既地方一路玩落去南邊時間充裕好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麗江同玉龍雪山都係我今次既目的之一, 希望去到. <br />\n但係6月天氣麻麻驚會落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0ef8b2eddb5b770a1dd169ef56ebc8682f0d0b","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求酒吧推介, 幾個麻甩佬應該會落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1f4cce13eef629ffea7a052e1a106d51b4d75c","tid":219960,"uid":65632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩"},{"pid":"5fb0ad02af386abb9c266779c16caae1a20c872f","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順"},{"pid":"d0842091ab05da439be0b09397f8ed45365ab2e4","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母話想去香格里拉，想做孝順仔帶佢去</blockquote><br />\n去拉, it's now or never <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67134578a85b4e282092ddac8636059eda0d8b77","tid":219960,"uid":65632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg"},{"pid":"8e6786790972fe2d553c326edba0ab8a8d7951df","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我地點都會去, 因為雨崩係我地雲南必去既CHECK list之一<br />\n巴打仲有無其它景點推介下？"},{"pid":"503748645da79167c54b6a62c1ee484757b765b1","tid":219960,"uid":6032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前聖誕去寄住朋友屋企，係昆明機場向南坐成5個鐘車先到。個陣好想去麗江同玉龍雪山，太遠最壞要坐成12個鐘車所以冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後個朋友同我講係昆明機場可以轉機去麗江，佢話如果我一早由最北既地方一路玩落去南邊時間充裕好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麗江同玉龍雪山都係我今次既目的之一, 希望去到. <br />\n但係6月天氣麻麻驚會落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講梅里雪山靚d未係點開發 天然d"},{"pid":"725f5ee353144cc570af0118ca82227e943c8154","tid":219960,"uid":65632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我地點都會去, 因為雨崩係我地雲南必去既CHECK list之一<br />\n巴打仲有無其它景點推介下？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好行之前操fit下<br />\n因為真係好辛苦 條路好斜 <br />\n行極都行唔完咁<br />\n其他景點: 松贊林寺，麗江古城，虎跳峽<br />\nbtw 香格里拉古城唔洗去 乜都冇"},{"pid":"42167197cff303e5ce4725a8a060cc86b3b1e1d0","tid":219960,"uid":105579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:47:43.000Z","msg":"六月去 十日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6285b35d269345788a35050fe09bd52c13097f2","tid":219960,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:52:48.000Z","msg":"自駕遊啊？"},{"pid":"3417784e6e3ad9daf318603e643f6c3c45ca9e62","tid":219960,"uid":88587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"請問巴打 <br />\n如果去五日的話有乜睇景地方必去"},{"pid":"6b2fc2a917e390f69eb2809327a4ef69d6674f30","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我地點都會去, 因為雨崩係我地雲南必去既CHECK list之一<br />\n巴打仲有無其它景點推介下？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好行之前操fit下<br />\n因為真係好辛苦 條路好斜 <br />\n行極都行唔完咁<br />\n其他景點: 松贊林寺，麗江古城，虎跳峽<br />\nbtw 香格里拉古城唔洗去 乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話要行幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格里拉古城燒完之後好似咩都冇,應該唔會去<br />\nBTW,個邊好似都係景多?有冇咩其他野玩?例如飲飲食食?"},{"pid":"5da925649591f2c59e2e2dcebefbcbfc6ddd4406","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六月去 十日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPLAN好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dda7fef7b1b5fc821c455a5da1c813e70e5da9","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自駕遊啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係啊, 應該到時拼車,3丁友"},{"pid":"e6341f4df900d3af6fc8fa7070c0727463784028","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問巴打 <br />\n如果去五日的話有乜睇景地方必去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5日好似唔多夠WO,<br />\n車程都冇一半"},{"pid":"66f64867a3d4e52c3b56565a4ea70d89bffc0741","tid":219960,"uid":88587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請問巴打 <br />\n如果去五日的話有乜睇景地方必去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5日好似唔多夠WO,<br />\n車程都冇一半</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打諗住去17日預幾多筆直"},{"pid":"d96bff79d424d3faa3489f0b0dfa88cbaa313c2f","tid":219960,"uid":56761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:01:26.000Z","msg":"去短期的話，昆明附近其實有好多值得去既地方，因為我幾鍾意佢地少數民族啲文化，有去到佢地個民族村，要買飛入，園區好大，唔買飛外面都好多野睇，買手信地方。<br />\n<br />\n冇時間去到麗江同再北既地方，可以近啲去昆明外邊既轎子雪山，唔太高天氣唔錯又有雪睇，啱一家大細去。<br />\n<br />\n不過北邊我比較少去，南方就去得多，不過想交通方便真係要自駕。"},{"pid":"c598f9eaf83c95487f8900a1ad77a49032999e8f","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請問巴打 <br />\n如果去五日的話有乜睇景地方必去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5日好似唔多夠WO,<br />\n車程都冇一半</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打諗住去17日預幾多筆直</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8000-1000我諗咩都夠, 都係窮遊"},{"pid":"9b57bcd27ba73e15af183c67ee0b2527b87e1975","tid":219960,"uid":66970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"之前去過有個叫紅土地嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n仲有西雙版納 都可以去下"},{"pid":"21351078eaeb7143ceebe84ffb3550d0b9e16116","tid":219960,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求酒吧推介, 幾個麻甩佬應該會落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n農民酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去完<br />\n必去地點:小布達拉宮，普達措，石卡神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古城可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e1bc95578bc7e619fe564a014204d126dc6d07","tid":219960,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求酒吧推介, 幾個麻甩佬應該會落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n農民酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去完<br />\n必去地點:小布達拉宮，普達措，石卡神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古城可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有一間羊肉同牦牛火鍋都好好食，160食到2-3個人傻下傻下，有人叫你去睇土司，你唔好去，好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e8be4f4437b951ea4567623aeb6c84ffdd6dd5","tid":219960,"uid":105579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>六月去 十日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPLAN好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未啊 不過一定會去麗江同香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雪山就仲諗緊 驚雨季上到去咩都睇唔到"},{"pid":"0c58b6d4195e18b9b678153b36072f9f16c88254","tid":219960