> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n農民酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去完<br />\n必去地點:小布達拉宮，普達措，石卡神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古城可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間酒吧有乜特色?<br />\n古城唔好去係咪因為太商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ae9683e0636bda2c5815b79b8351039b80933d","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>六月去 十日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPLAN好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未啊 不過一定會去麗江同香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雪山就仲諗緊 驚雨季上到去咩都睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔去埋雨崩?不過時間好似有趕。<br />\n我都驚到時會落雨"},{"pid":"d6eecd074a0766b498aacf1c641ff024d3c2d5db","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>12月-1月去左11日 跨年<br />\n有4日係行雨崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我地點都會去, 因為雨崩係我地雲南必去既CHECK list之一<br />\n巴打仲有無其它景點推介下？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好行之前操fit下<br />\n因為真係好辛苦 條路好斜 <br />\n行極都行唔完咁<br />\n其他景點: 松贊林寺，麗江古城，虎跳峽<br />\nbtw 香格里拉古城唔洗去 乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話要行幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格里拉古城燒完之後好似咩都冇,應該唔會去<br />\nBTW,個邊好似都係景多?有冇咩其他野玩?例如飲飲食食?</blockquote><br />\n雨崩行4日<br />\n飲飲食食麗江啦 香格里拉荒蕪到連m記都冇</blockquote><br />\n 自從香格燒完之後好似都唔太值得去?"},{"pid":"6c537718c4528496c8aa841e6ecd5fb8f912748d","tid":219960,"uid":56452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我地點都會去, 因為雨崩係我地雲南必去既CHECK list之一<br />\n巴打仲有無其它景點推介下？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好行之前操fit下<br />\n因為真係好辛苦 條路好斜 <br />\n行極都行唔完咁<br />\n其他景點: 松贊林寺，麗江古城，虎跳峽<br />\nbtw 香格里拉古城唔洗去 乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話要行幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格里拉古城燒完之後好似咩都冇,應該唔會去<br />\nBTW,個邊好似都係景多?有冇咩其他野玩?例如飲飲食食?</blockquote><br />\n雨崩行4日<br />\n飲飲食食麗江啦 香格里拉荒蕪到連m記都冇</blockquote><br />\n 自從香格燒完之後好似都唔太值得去?</blockquote><br />\n香格里拉留一日都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔值得專登去，除非你去雨崩就可以留一留"},{"pid":"b6bfb929403e13384f0e9ba7683f682122878b6d","tid":219960,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe5fda9f4dd32fbc624a1e371d4daaa82ea6286","tid":219960,"uid":56452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，雲南發生左單新聞之後個邊風氣好差<br />\n好多大陸人都叫人唔好去<br />\n巴打自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928e9b45ed56c21fbe6c9ab3343f298a5be4b3fa","tid":219960,"uid":52130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"六月中去11日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429855f3218a5630150df78434c2d27d3c291917","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，雲南發生左單新聞之後個邊風氣好差<br />\n好多大陸人都叫人唔好去<br />\n巴打自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔撚係下話，機票都買埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7282829cc77cda14e6c91bf3d3fa0423ef5998","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六月中去11日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nplan好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871e143fd8a9f73415a2f00e897ccca74be2ae09","tid":219960,"uid":62602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"去咁多日去埋稻城亞丁都夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190df16eb8fc7e96ec9eeac521cd943d5b3a5c5e","tid":219960,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求酒吧推介, 幾個麻甩佬應該會落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n農民酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去完<br />\n必去地點:小布達拉宮，普達措，石卡神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古城可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間酒吧有乜特色?<br />\n古城唔好去係咪因為太商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係香格里拉冇乜夜生活，個間酒吧係客棧老細帶我地去，客棧老細幾Nice，古城唔去原因係，忽忽都整路，又冇野睇，地盤咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68bef0bd495dc12d1b5fb6e78fe8ed0aed39609","tid":219960,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求酒吧推介, 幾個麻甩佬應該會落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n農民酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去完<br />\n必去地點:小布達拉宮，普達措，石卡神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古城可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間酒吧有乜特色?<br />\n古城唔好去係咪因為太商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係香格里拉冇乜夜生活，個間酒吧係客棧老細帶我地去，客棧老細幾Nice，古城唔去原因係，忽忽都整路，又冇野睇，地盤咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c5ce97fcc3e8de33836750467a9fdf5099e68d","tid":219960,"uid":52130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>六月中去11日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nplan好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係去麗江 瀘沽湖 香格里拉 飛來寺大路野<br />\n想去瀘沽湖租返日電單車環湖 但好似話依家禁曬唔比租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299bb0e19d35a6ccf62d8ea79f75d2066c392d3d","tid":219960,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcd311716b464b24dd564be5da15d116db69000b","tid":219960,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"我上次都係去十七日<br />\n唔多夠皮，昆明無玩到，香格里拉石卡雪山一定要去！好靚！"},{"pid":"89a267e609b455bce340938693a621e1a70d96ad","tid":219960,"uid":21538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上次都係去十七日<br />\n唔多夠皮，昆明無玩到，香格里拉石卡雪山一定要去！好靚！</blockquote><br />\n我打算今年十二月/下一月去"},{"pid":"c1311676fa078ede0c246e31d9e0f03067947a88","tid":219960,"uid":71840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，雲南發生左單新聞之後個邊風氣好差<br />\n好多大陸人都叫人唔好去<br />\n巴打自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱去完雲南無嘢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玉龍雪山好多人 淡季排隊搭車轉車前後都兩個幾鐘頭 上到頂影相位好細 <br />\n反而藍月谷唔錯 上面有巴打影得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麗江古城好商業化 可以去下酒吧 不過十二點就要靜音唔可以係台唱歌打鼓 <br />\n大理嘅雙廊修路 大塵冇嘢睇啲路好難行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26235c9fd5cebd949d3c6a9a55c361273ea455f4","tid":219960,"uid":71840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"瀘沽湖好靚 值得留三日以上 不過唔好join團 得2日1夜團 會有購物買銀時間 冇咩時間俾你自由走動影靚相 <br />\n<br />\n去完十一日都唔夠喉 冇時間去香格里拉就返香港 一齊去嘅朋友去埋香格里拉話好靚 好後悔冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be54272e7570a8e37e9e74b7bedd8a70824d808a","tid":219960,"uid":44007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"巴打筆直幾多<br />\n利申可能年尾去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 參考下"},{"pid":"f552c40fa4d9376438ed43ae27cf775781c37bbd","tid":219960,"uid":65632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打行入去會唔會好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我D FD平時都冇做開運動,驚頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n辛苦 我去果時溫度0下 冇乜人去<br />\n夏天去係旺季 但落雨機會大<br />\n冇做開運動但想挑戰下自己都可以去既<br />\n但有人唔想去就唔好格硬去了<br />\n咪到時高山反應/扭親整親就gg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗我地點都會去, 因為雨崩係我地雲南必去既CHECK list之一<br />\n巴打仲有無其它景點推介下？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好行之前操fit下<br />\n因為真係好辛苦 條路好斜 <br />\n行極都行唔完咁<br />\n其他景點: 松贊林寺，麗江古城，虎跳峽<br />\nbtw 香格里拉古城唔洗去 乜都冇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話要行幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格里拉古城燒完之後好似咩都冇,應該唔會去<br />\nBTW,個邊好似都係景多?有冇咩其他野玩?例如飲飲食食?</blockquote><br />\n雨崩行4日<br />\n飲飲食食麗江啦 香格里拉荒蕪到連m記都冇</blockquote><br />\n 自從香格燒完之後好似都唔太值得去?</blockquote><br />\n香格里拉留一日都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔值得專登去，除非你去雨崩就可以留一留</blockquote><br />\nyes 香格里拉比我感覺好荒蕪 熱水又唔穩定 最普通既快餐店都冇間 唯一值得去下係松贊林寺 本身行完雨崩plan左留香格里拉兩日(買左機票香格里拉返昆明) 但經過係香格里拉準備去雨崩既日子 最後都係改左去麗江(唔理張機票 買過麗江返昆明)"},{"pid":"a1363acd7ec8ec92e1a19302ba586366951699ea","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>六月中去11日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nplan好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係去麗江 瀘沽湖 香格里拉 飛來寺大路野<br />\n想去瀘沽湖租返日電單車環湖 但好似話依家禁曬唔比租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n租單車踩有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbed844893d31a1bb8a714b1952231709eae179","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會.去左5日香格理拉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客棧老細好NICE.<br />\n個生活好正.<br />\n唔好睇香格里拉多野睇.<br />\n有間酒吧好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求酒吧推介, 幾個麻甩佬應該會落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格理拉燒之前令好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n農民酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月去完<br />\n必去地點:小布達拉宮，普達措，石卡神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古城可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間酒吧有乜特色?<br />\n古城唔好去係咪因為太商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係香格里拉冇乜夜生活，個間酒吧係客棧老細帶我地去，客棧老細幾Nice，古城唔去原因係，忽忽都整路，又冇野睇，地盤咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢d古城我諗黎黎去去都係咁上次下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f164701e2468bcfb597cde5944aa5f6718e88f59","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真，雲南發生左單新聞之後個邊風氣好差<br />\n好多大陸人都叫人唔好去<br />\n巴打自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽fd講，有單新聞，係有個女仔比個邊d土霸打到面都毀容</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地幾條仔去應該無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20f121c4f6d44d0dceeabfde4da3a6317f62224","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上次都係去十七日<br />\n唔多夠皮，昆明無玩到，香格里拉石卡雪山一定要去！好靚！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢d必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有無其他小眾d ge 景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f650d5083f9479c0df0548a51f386ec274c11539","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打筆直幾多<br />\n利申可能年尾去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 參考下</blockquote><br />\n8000-1000，我之前見有人兩個星期5000搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過係淡季"},{"pid":"da02cd0a4ba781c42ad599e21a7102dd6f87b637","tid":219960,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"去過三次雲南，全部自己玩<br />\n麗江 香格里拉 瀘沽湖都最少去過二次，不同季節<br />\n<br />\n推介小人去既，中虎跳，咪撚去上虎跳，垃圾來<br />\n其餘大路野就唔講了，<br />\n<br />\n雲南都要跟local tour 正傻仔<br />\n交通易到不得了"},{"pid":"259861ad72728d5271f93e82cef3101691a5703e","tid":219960,"uid":42328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"六月頭至中應該去兩個禮拜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夾到可以拼車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb28c7ac49deb1f90b1989d7bf4ba1942060502","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六月頭至中應該去兩個禮拜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夾到可以拼車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好吖，我去到6月10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acbe3d2b2571041eff2926fc7d1ee7b46581556","tid":219960,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"如果想一個人去 會唔會危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0039fbac38a4463d756e54e9c7fb965ae30e20","tid":219960,"uid":33871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"六月尾去15日🤘🏾🤘🏾"},{"pid":"94b40e21b4016ee47c33f09270a1a19386b074a7","tid":219960,"uid":1370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f9b4106e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow</a><br />\n一齊交通下"},{"pid":"2a838a3ca18f867647db2229fbf95595dde78082","tid":219960,"uid":1370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f9b4106e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow</a><br />\n一齊交<span style=\"color: red;\">流</span>下</blockquote>"},{"pid":"79c6c928f966c5fb5954489e82e3664c968459ec","tid":219960,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"七月中求旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576a76111fa1a777413b2cfa0533885023de38c9","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f9b4106e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAtnvTnXel4KRlefow</a><br />\n一齊交<span style=\"color: red;\">流</span>下</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee6c1569d6ef3986febbc2c6dd04b2c350402d9","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果想一個人去 會唔會危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見好多巴打都係自己一個，應該無問題，雖然我自己就三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad91be84078272d939f9a7855f6ec42fe58da6f8","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六月尾去15日🤘🏾🤘🏾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nplan好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dfad702a8b333d2ce6f20efc91a0914c5461ad","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>七月中求旅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去到六月渣，可惜可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5960d6479739892dcd544b9f5153a6253067059","tid":219960,"uid":30962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s308mu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs308mu.jpg&h=15e02fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行緊上雨崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n詳細資料可以睇我之前個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我行雨崩係我人生第二次行山，好撚辛苦，西當條路斜到乜咁 唔係講笑 話唔辛苦係呃人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過好值得"},{"pid":"d0222974cae4ea43d5aab871294459956d14f08f","tid":219960,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s308mu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs308mu.jpg&h=15e02fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行緊上雨崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n詳細資料可以睇我之前個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我行雨崩係我人生第二次行山，好撚辛苦，西當條路斜到乜咁 唔係講笑 話唔辛苦係呃人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過好值得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雨崩到時都會去 但係驚落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91a92fe9c8a1c32894de8958e6078e594613ccc","tid":219960,"uid":21538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:54:17.000Z","msg":"1月去 有冇問題？"}]}